{"tid":1163173,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"唔講政治，香港呢廿年黎都無左好多優勢","createTime":"2019-05-20T09:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T19:14:00.000Z","uid":47466,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc2ec76c2751fe1b00d94f6a7924e8c672e785b","tid":1163173,"uid":47466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"我細細個老師/大陸個班親戚都會吹噓香港有幾好，但今日睇翻其實無撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎好快變做一個普通中國市。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.美食天堂</span><br />\n我諗金融海嘯之前，街上面既鋪頭會賣好多唔同野食，有缽仔糕，雞蛋仔，腸粉，雲吞麵呢類傳統小店，放學成日都去呢d鋪頭到食野吹水，價錢唔貴，而且真係好好食，但租太貴就殺左好多呢d(傳統小食)鋪頭。 依家00後都唔知有無食過缽仔糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，出左黎做野，食茶餐廳樣樣野都係汁撈飯，好少選擇，全部都係咖喱豬排飯個類，無益重口味。以前我比30蚊食茶記，最少都有好多蒸餸既選擇，雲耳蒸滑雞，荷葉蒸飯。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.英語水平</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人其實英文一直都唔太差既，一般服務行業最少都溝通到，我老細係外國人有一次走左入sasa想問佢個隻C朗香水邊到有得買，順便傾下計問下多唔多人買個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢同我講翻佢地好緊張，都指到d香水起邊，但就無答到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗依家服務業serve得大陸人太多，英文都已經唔重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前政府條宣傳片都會講welcome to hong kong~<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有交通方便同埋有效率，但大家都好清楚港鐵同個4000蚊，所以都唔打咁多字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde3c2ebac86ea7773302e8040c97ffa0c347943","tid":1163173,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bb5fcad2ef8ecd8116523258c449d5c66220a8","tid":1163173,"uid":77143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美食天堂唔係咁解"},{"pid":"771c2b0d4a2fdf576145cc326016685fe2c3743c","tid":1163173,"uid":81273,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:56:23.000Z","msg":"1. 美食天堂<br />\n有錢依舊係咩都有得你食<br />\n2.英語水平<br />\n而家既零售業前線九成係新移民擔大旗 英咩文姐"},{"pid":"0a1121ee75097b3935dc0baf55e3c9090081bb7c","tid":1163173,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:56:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71c147a91aaffe51c3002259ac9f62e99bb26c97","tid":1163173,"uid":43314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:16:49.000Z","msg":"全部都係政策造成，最後都係政治"},{"pid":"87b900317d1801a01b749be40a3e0234321812aa","tid":1163173,"uid":32549,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:19:57.000Z","msg":"慢慢變番緊美食天堂，漸漸開緊舖<br />\n<br />\n未來英文有乜用？外國人已經學緊普通話"},{"pid":"5ebcee21d08bd54c00acff74ad11356f4b919e78","tid":1163173,"uid":218729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfc2ec76c2751fe1b00d94f6a7924e8c672e785b","tid":1163173,"uid":47466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"我細細個老師/大陸個班親戚都會吹噓香港有幾好，但今日睇翻其實無撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎好快變做一個普通中國市。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.美食天堂</span><br />\n我諗金融海嘯之前，街上面既鋪頭會賣好多唔同野食，有缽仔糕，雞蛋仔，腸粉，雲吞麵呢類傳統小店，放學成日都去呢d鋪頭到食野吹水，價錢唔貴，而且真係好好食，但租太貴就殺左好多呢d(傳統小食)鋪頭。 依家00後都唔知有無食過缽仔糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm